\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces LOCALE pipeline overview. Phase 1 constructs ego graphs and queries the LLM $K{=}10$ times per node to collect soft vote distributions. Phase 2 compiles non-collider constraints into a weighted Max-2SAT problem. Phase 3 reconciles dual-endpoint votes per edge. Phase 4 applies a safety valve ensuring the final output $\vec  {G}$ never degrades below the Phase 1 baseline.}}{3}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:method}{{1}{3}{LOCALE pipeline overview. Phase 1 constructs ego graphs and queries the LLM $K{=}10$ times per node to collect soft vote distributions. Phase 2 compiles non-collider constraints into a weighted Max-2SAT problem. Phase 3 reconciles dual-endpoint votes per edge. Phase 4 applies a safety valve ensuring the final output $\vec {G}$ never degrades below the Phase 1 baseline}{figure.1}{}}
